              "text-align": "center",
              "color": "#232323"
            }
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"11\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><div><b>How Does Burn Tide Work?</b></div></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                    Enter your subtitle here\n                </h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Burn Tide is designed to support the body's natural metabolism by combining six carefully selected ingredients that help promote energy, healthy fat utilization, and overall wellness. Rather than relying on harsh stimulants, Burn Tide works with the body's natural processes to support a balanced and active lifestyle.\n<br>\n<br>At the core of the formula are Apple Cider Vinegar and BHB Salts, two ingredients commonly used to support metabolic health. Apple Cider Vinegar helps support healthy digestion and feelings of fullness, while BHB Salts provide an alternative energy source that may help support sustained energy throughout the day.\n<br>\n<br>To further support metabolism, Burn Tide includes Green Tea Extract and Cayenne Pepper. These ingredients are known for supporting thermogenesis, the body's natural process of converting stored energy into usable fuel, helping maintain a healthy metabolic rate.\n<br>\n<br>The formula also features L-Carnitine and Pomegranate Extract. L-Carnitine plays a key role in transporting fatty acids to be used for energy, while Pomegranate Extract delivers powerful antioxidant support to help protect and maintain healthy cells.\n<br>\n<br>Together, these ingredients create a comprehensive daily formula designed to support healthy weight-management goals, balanced energy levels, appetite control, and long-term metabolic wellness when combined with a healthy diet and regular physical activity.&nbsp;<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
