          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Article Title</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                    Enter your subtitle here\n                </h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Burntide is formulated with a powerful blend of science-backed ingredients designed to support healthy metabolism, sustained energy, and overall wellness. Featuring Apple Cider Vinegar, BHB Salts, Green Tea Extract, Cayenne Pepper, L-Carnitine, and Pomegranate Extract, this advanced formula works to support metabolic function, energy production, and healthy fat utilization.&nbsp;<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vixzSzA3Qo",
          "_anchor": "content5-7d",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".counter-container": {
              "ul": {
                "margin": "0",
                "list-style": "none",
                "padding-left": "2.5rem",
                "li": {
                  "margin-bottom": "1rem",
                  "position": "relative",
                  "& when (@stylizedCounters)": {
                    "list-style": "none",
                    "position": "relative",
                    "padding-left": "1rem",
                    "&:before": {
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "left": "-40px",
                      "content": "\"\"",
                      "display": "flex",
                      "justify-content": "center",
                      "align-items": "center",
                      "color": "contrast(@iconColor)",
                      "background-color": "@iconColor",
                      "width": "40px",
                      "height": "40px",
                      "border-radius": "50%",
                      "margin-top": "5px",
                      "& when (@countersType = \"circle\")": {
                        "background": "none",
                        "border": "1px solid @iconColor",
                        "color": "@iconColor"
                      },
                      "& when (@countersType = \"square\")": {
                        "border-radius": "0"
                      },
                      "& when (@mark)": {
                        "content": "\"✓\""
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  "& when not (@stylizedCounters)": {
                    "&:before": {
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "left": "-1.6rem",
                      "content": "\"\\2022\"",
                      "color": "@iconColor",
                      "font-weight": "bold",
                      "font-size": "2rem",
                      "width": "1.6rem",
                      "line-height": "1.2"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "_name": "content8",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content8\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Stylized\" name=\"stylizedCounters\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Mark\" name=\"mark\" checked condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n        <select title=\"Type\" name=\"countersType\" condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n            <option value=\"default\" selected>Сircle Fill</option>\n            <option value=\"circle\">Circle</option>\n            <option value=\"square\">Square</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#a4192a\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"counter-container col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                    Shape your future web project with the Mobirise app.\n                </h4>\n                <div class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 20rem) / 28));\">Supports Healthy Fat Metabolism and Weight Management: </b><span style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 20rem) / 28));\">JellyThin is formulated to support the body's natural metabolic processes and healthy fat utilization. By combining carefully selected ingredients such as Apple Cider Vinegar and BHB Ketone Salts, JellyThin helps complement healthy eating habits and active lifestyles, making it easier to stay focused on long-term weight management goals.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 20rem) / 28));\"><b>Helps Control Cravings and Appetite:</b>&nbsp;Persistent cravings and unnecessary snacking can make it difficult to maintain healthy lifestyle habits. JellyThin is designed to support appetite balance and promote feelings of satisfaction between meals, helping individuals make mindful dietary choices and stay committed to their wellness objectives.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 20rem) / 28));\"><b>Provides Clean, Sustained Daily Energy:</b>&nbsp;Unlike stimulant-heavy products that may lead to energy spikes and crashes, JellyThin supports steady energy production throughout the day. Its wellness-focused formula helps individuals maintain daily vitality, productivity, and motivation without relying on harsh stimulants or excessive caffeine.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 20rem) / 28));\"><b>Supports Digestive Health and Overall Wellness:</b>&nbsp;Healthy digestion plays an important role in nutrient absorption, metabolic function, and overall well-being. JellyThin includes ingredients commonly associated with digestive wellness, helping support a balanced approach to health while complementing broader wellness goals.</span></li><li><b>Promotes Focus, Clarity, and Active Living:</b> Maintaining mental focus and motivation is essential when pursuing health and fitness goals. JellyThin supports overall wellness by helping individuals stay energized, engaged, and focused throughout the day, making it easier to maintain healthy routines and active lifestyles.</li><li><b>Supports Cellular Energy Production:</b> The formula contains BHB Salts and L-Carnitine, two ingredients known for their role in energy metabolism. These compounds help support the body's natural ability to produce energy at the cellular level, contributing to overall vitality, physical performance, and daily wellness. Efficient cellular energy production is essential for maintaining an active lifestyle and supporting long-term health.</li><li><b>Supports Appetite and Craving Control:</b> Managing food cravings and maintaining healthy eating habits can be challenging. Burntide includes ingredients traditionally used to support feelings of fullness and satisfaction between meals. This additional support may help individuals stay focused on their nutritional goals and make healthier dietary choices throughout the day.</li><li><b>Promotes Thermogenic Activity:</b> Green Tea Extract and Cayenne Pepper are commonly used in metabolic wellness formulas because of their ability to support thermogenesis, the body's natural process of generating heat and utilizing energy. Supporting thermogenic activity may help encourage healthy calorie utilization and contribute to overall metabolic efficiency.</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
