          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"11\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Article Title</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Conclusion</b></h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Burn Tide offers a convenient and stimulant-free approach to supporting healthy weight-management goals, metabolism, and daily energy levels. With a thoughtfully crafted blend of Apple Cider Vinegar, BHB Salts, Green Tea Extract, Cayenne Pepper, L-Carnitine, and Pomegranate Extract, the formula is designed to support the body's natural fat-utilization and energy-producing processes while promoting overall wellness.\n<br>\n<br>Unlike many weight-management products that rely on harsh stimulants, Burn Tide focuses on providing balanced metabolic support through research-backed ingredients in a delicious, easy-to-take gummy format. Whether your goal is to support a healthy metabolism, maintain steady energy, manage cravings, or complement an active lifestyle, Burn Tide offers a simple addition to your daily wellness routine.\n<br>\n<br>When combined with proper nutrition, regular exercise, and healthy lifestyle habits, Burn Tide can be a valuable tool for individuals looking to stay consistent with their long-term health and wellness goals. Its convenient formula, quality ingredients, and comprehensive metabolic support make Burn Tide a practical choice for those seeking a healthier, more energized lifestyle.&nbsp;<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
